biri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                            Learn more\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-12 col-md-{{videoWidth}} video-block\">\n                <div mbr-video class=\"mbr-figure\">\n                    <iframe src=\"https://youtu.be/pSOCQREqXac?loop=1&autoplay=1\"></iframe>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"mbr-description mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showDescription\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-description\">\n                    Shadows dance, creativity transcends\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
